modules.description: This module defines types and functions for constructing and manipulating Software Heritage identifiers (SWHIDs). It supports operations to create identifiers for content, directories, snapshots, revisions, and releases, each with optional qualifiers like context or line fragments. The module works with string-based object IDs and structured types representing Merkle DAG nodes, paths, and origins, enabling precise referencing of software artifacts in version-controlled repositories.
